                                            Partial        Financial
                          Operating       operating          trading
                             profit*         profit**         income***
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Deutsche Bank          3.6bn (-15%)     4.7bn (-8%)      543m (-63%)
Dresdner Bank          1.3bn (-17%)    2.8bn (+17%)    -301m (-156%)
