</XX>
<CN>USZ  United States of America.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P3411 Metal Cans.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>MGMT  Management &amp; Marketing.
    MKTS  Production.
</TP>
