<HEADLINE>
FT  20 DEC 94 / Accountants gain share issue role
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Chartered accountants can act as sponsors for the issue or sale of company
shares and securities, the Chartered Accountants Joint Ethics Committee has
announced.
The move follows changes announced earlier this year by the London Stock
Exchange allowing accounting firms to act as sponsors.
