<TEXT>
Pirelli, the Italian tyres and cables manufacturer, yesterday launched its
first manufacturing site in the Far East. The joint venture with a
subsidiary of Gajah Tunggal, a diversified Indonesian group, will produce
and sell energy and telecommunication cables and systems in Indonesia. Half
the venture will be owned by Pirelli Cables and the other half by PT
